t-family:\">北区浮动盘管换热器维修等</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">项目。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:22pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">2.2项目地点：盐城市第一人民医院北区</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">（毓龙西路166号）</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:22pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">2.3招标内容：</span><span style=\"font-family:\">北区浮动盘管换热器更换换热管、1#立式半容积式热交换器更换换热管等维修项目，</span><span style=\"font-family:\">具体内容详见招标人要求和工程量清单</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:22pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">2.4发包方式：包工包料。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:22pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">3、投标人资格要求</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:22pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">3.1 投标</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">人</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">须是</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">具有建设行政主管部门核发的建筑机电安装工程专业承包三级及以上资质</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">的</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">独立法人</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">，</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">并具有</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">有效的安全生产许证</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">；</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:22pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">3.2 投标</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">人</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">须</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; font-family:\">具有中华人民共和国特种设备安装改造维修许可证（压力容器）或中华人民共和国特种设备制造许可证（压力容器）；</span></p><p style=\"line-height:22pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:24pt; widows:0; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:\">.3</span><span style=\"font-family:\">投标时须授权技术人员参加本项目谈判。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:22pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">4、投标报名及招标文件的获取</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:22pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">请符合上述资质条件的投标人携带单位介绍信（或授权委托书，须注明联系人、电话及邮箱）原件到江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司造价二部（盐城市青年西路8号8楼805室）投标报名，投标报名时间2020年9月17日8时至2020年9月21日18时。联系人：刘永杰，0515-85606510；手机：13626222271。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:22pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">5、本项目采用竞争性谈判方式。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:22pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">6、投标申请人有违反《盐城市市场廉政准则规定（试行）》中规定情形的，招标人将拒绝投标报名。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:22pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">7、招投标监督管理机构及投诉电话：盐城市第一人民医院纪检监察室，联系电话0515-</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">66696810</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:22pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">其余内容详见招标文件。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; margin-bottom:5pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:5pt; text-align:right; \"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; margin-bottom:5pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:5pt; text-align:right; \"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">时间：</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">2020</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">年</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">9月17</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">日</span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff; color:#000000; font-family:\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p><p><br /></p>\',\n  ),\n  \'assist_category\' => \'\',\n  \'url\' => \'\',\n  \'author\' => \'\',\n  \'list_order\' => \'2020-09-17\',\n  \'timestamp\' => \'2020-09-17\',\n  \'verify\' => 1,\n  \'credit\' => \'\',\n  \'html_view_url_rule\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_description\' => \'\',\n  \'template\' => \'\',\n  \'model\' => \'article\',\n  \'verified\' => \'\',\n  \'id\' => \'\',\n  \'iid\' => \'\',\n  \'page\' => \'\',\n  \'_referer\' => \'http://127.0.0.1/admin.php/cms/item-add\',\n  \'action\' => \'add\',\n  \'attachment_hash\' => \'7b9e727477eaedc0\',\n  \'views\' => \'534\',\n  \'verifier\' => \'ycyyo\',\n)','1654844687');
INSERT INTO `p8_admin_log` (`id`,`uid`,`system`,`module`,`action`,`iid`,`cid`,`site`,`username`,`title`,`url`,`ip`,`data`,`timestamp`) VALUES ('6043','5','cms','item','add','0','859','','ycyyo','添加内容 | 盐城市第一人民医院北区6号楼2楼西侧病房装修改造工程设计服务项目招','/admin.php/cms/item-add','172.16.1.2','array (\n  \'__referer\' => \'http://192.168.162.72/admin.php/cms/item-add?model=article\',\n  \'cid\' => \'859\',\n  \'title\' => \'盐城市第一人民医院北区6号楼2楼西侧病房装修改造工程设计服务项目招标公告\',\n  \'title_color\' => \'\',\n  \'sub_title\' => \'\',\n  \'source\' => \'总务处\',\n  \'keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'frame\' => \'\',\n  \'summary\' => \'\',\n  \'addon_title\' => \'\',\n  \'#field_content_posted\' => \'\',\n  \'field#\' => \n  array (\n    \'content\' => \'<br /><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">1、项目概况</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">1.1项目名称：盐城市第一人民医院北区6号楼2楼西侧病房装修改造工程设计服务项目；</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">1.2建设地点：盐城市第一人民医院北区（毓龙西路166号）；</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">1.3工程规模：盐城市第一人民医院北区</span><span style=\"font-family:\">6号楼</span><span style=\"font-family:\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:\">F西侧</span><span style=\"font-family:\">病房</span><span style=\"font-family:\">装修</span><span style=\"font-family:\">改造工程，改造总面积约</span><span style=\"font-family:\">94</span><span style=\"font-family:\">0平方米，详见设计任务书。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">1.4招标内容：盐城市第一人民医院北区6号楼2楼西侧病区装修改造工程设计服务，包含但不限于方案设计、施工图设计以及施工和保修等阶段设计咨询服务等，具体以招标人的书面通知为准。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">1.5质量标准：符合国家、省及市关于施工图设计深度的规范要求，并满足《建筑工程设计文件编制深度规定(2016年版)》，最终设计成果须确保通过相关部门审查。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">1.6设计时限：满足招标人要求。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">2、投标人资格要求</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">2.1投标人具备独立企业法人资格；</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">2.2投标人须是具有建设主管部门核发的建筑装饰工程设计专项乙级及以上或工程设计综合甲级资质的独立法人；</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">2.3项目负责人须是本单位在职职工，并具有工程类高级职称。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">2.4本次招标不接受联合体投标。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">3、投标报名</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">请符合上述资质条件的投标人携带单位介绍信（或授权委托书，须注明联系人、电话及邮箱）原件到江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司造价二部（盐城市青年西路8号8楼</span><span style=\"font-family:\">805</span><span style=\"font-family:\">室）投标报名，投标报名时间2020年9月</span><span style=\"font-family:\">17</span><span style=\"font-family:\">日8时至2020年9月</span><span style=\"font-family:\">21</span><span style=\"font-family:\">日18时。联系人：刘永杰，0515-85606510；手机：13626222271。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">4、本项目采用资格后审</span><span style=\"font-family:\">，</span><span style=\"font-family:\">综合评估法。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">5、投标申请人有违反《盐城市市场廉政准则规定（试行）》中规定情形的，招标人将拒绝投标报名。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">6、招投标监督管理机构及投诉电话：盐城市第一人民医院纪检监察室，联系电话0515-66696810。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">具体内容详见招标文件。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-align:right; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-align:right; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">时间：2020年9月</span><span style=\"font-family:\">17</span><span style=\"font-family:\">日</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0; \"><br /></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">30</span></p><p><br /></p>\',\n  ),\n  \'assist_category\' => \'\',\n  \'url\' => \'\',\n  \'author\' => \'\',\n  \'list_order\' => \'2020-09-17\',\n  \'timestamp\' => \'2020-09-17\',\n  \'verify\' => 1,\n  \'credit\' => \'\',\n  \'html_view_url_rule\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_description\' => \'\',\n  \'template\' => \'\',\n  \'model\' => \'article\',\n  \'verified\' => \'\',\n  \'id\' => \'\',\n  \'iid\' => \'\',\n  \'page\' => \'\',\n  \'_referer\' => \'http://127.0.0.1/admin.php/cms/item-add\',\n  \'action\' => \'add\',\n  \'attachment_hash\' => \'73cf0b150b278dbd\',\n  \'views\' => \'331\',\n  \'verif